desc:
You get a Raspberry Pi if you win. No, not the food one. That's all we can say for now. 
Here are the rules -
a) Robot must be a ground wheeled vehicle; 
length must be maximum of 20 cm; 
width must be maximum of 20 cm; 
weight must be maximum of 4kg; 
power must be maximum of 24 volts on-board power supply.
b) Metal wheeled robot are not acceptable, each team must use rubberized wheels.
c) Each team (maximum of 3 members) must bring its own power supply and backups for robot, no additional equipment/parts will be supplied.
d) No wireless communication or external data feed to robot will be allowed.

Registration Fee of BDT 300 Per Team is applicable. You will have to pay on the event day.

